title: Lisa Bilyeu
description:
In this episode Ellen sits down with Lisa Bilyeu. Lisa is the co-founder of Quest nutrition, co-founder and president of Impact Theory, and the host of Women of Impact. They discuss not letting fear stop you, how to use negativity as fuel, and her new book, Radical Confidence.
